text: Édouard Beaudoin Jr. was an archer from France. Beaudoin competed at the 1900 Summer Olympics and the 1908 Summer Olympics.Édouard BeaudoinÉdouard BEAUDOIN, JR. == References == Category:Year of birth missing Category:Year of death missing Category:French archers Category:Olympians for France
